E_D("replace into `ecs_goods` values('118','6','ECS000118','倩碧润肤露 (有油版1，2) 125ml','+','158','5','','98','0.000','174.00','145.00','0.00','0','0','1','','','<p>碧润肤露有油型，倩碧润肤露为您提供肌肤所需要的各种养分，有效精心呵护您的肌肤。</p>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"660\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" width=\"85\"><b>商品名称：</b></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" width=\"250\"><span>倩碧润肤露 (有油版1,2) 125ml</span></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"bottom\" rowspan=\"7\" align=\"right\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"倩碧润肤露 (有油版1，2) 125ml\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201305/1c7b7f8aaea899a8672212ba56a3c50e.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\"><b>品 牌：</b></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\"><span itemprop=\"brand\">倩碧 (Clinique)</span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\"><b>功 效：</b></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\"><span>保湿,滋润,柔肤</span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\"><b>产品容量：</b></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\"><span>125ml</span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\"><b>适用人群：</b></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\"><span>有油的黄油比较适合干性肌肤使用。</span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\"><b>保质期限：</b></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\"><span>3年（具体日期以收到的实物为准）</span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\"><b>产品包装：</b></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\"><span>本产品为全新有盒无塑封。（多款包装，随机发货）！</span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div id=\"story\" class=\"deal_contents\">\r\n<div id=\"title_story\" class=\"block_title\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51); font-size: medium\"><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201305/049d34716456a0840aea523f4dc7b404.jpg\" /></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51); font-size: medium\"><strong>有效防止肌肤水分流失及过敏现象</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: small\"><font size=\"2\">配方与肌肤自然滋润成分如出一辙，复制天然的水油平衡状态，让肌肤即刻变成擅长导入养分的湿海绵。</font></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51); font-size: large\"><font size=\"2\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201305/3b7c89a18f8cf94a17774b2b9bb39032.jpg\" /></font></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(102,102,102)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\"><span style=\"font-size: medium\"><strong>自然清新不油腻</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: small\"><font size=\"2\">被称之为皮肤的甘露，保持了倩碧的一贯品质和风格，能唤醒皮肤，制造适量水分及改善皮肤天然滋润保护膜，以提供额外滋润。将带来全天候的滋润感觉，不油不腻，连痘痘皮肤也可以安心使用。</font></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: small\"><font size=\"2\"><img alt=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: medium\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201305/386e8ad44059a66461f578f5cd1ae65d.jpg\" /><br />\r\n</font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(102,102,102)\"><span style=\"font-size: medium\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">有效恢复皮肤水分平衡</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: small\"><font size=\"2\">根本上帮助滋润品的吸收，安全有效，它通过了最严格的过敏性测试，100%不含香料。保持肌肤水油平衡。其中乳液配方特效的含油配方，给您多一点的滋润。能迅速深入滋润肌肤，令其恢复柔软、润滑、充满光泽。</font></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: small\"><font size=\"2\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201305/3afbe869d51dec7ace41fe51a3e61c3f.jpg\" /><br />\r\n</font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium\">特别说明</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: small\">本次团购的黄油产地有英国和美国两种，具体区别为：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102,102,102)\"><strong>外盒大小</strong>：英国生产盒子较大，上有MADE in UK 字样。美国生产盒子较小，上有MADE in USA字样。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102,102,102)\"><strong>说明书</strong>：英国版有说明书，美国版的没有说明书。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102,102,102)\"><strong>印刷字体</strong>：英国版较粗，美国版较细。此外英国版和美国版外盒排版和瓶子上印刷也有所不同。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102,102,102)\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201305/889806ac5c38423f9fcc803e3377925a.jpg\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id=\"usage\" class=\"deal_contents\">\r\n<div id=\"title_usage\" class=\"block_title\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>早、晚各一次，于洁肤水之后使用，可用于任何干燥部位。（对于油性肌肤可能只需用于眼部周围和颈部）。</p>\r\n<p><strong>温馨提示：</strong>护肤品成分各有不同，敏感性肌肤的人士请先在耳后进行测试后再使用哦！<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201305/1d1e428a2dd72ecec6da3298b52d2611.jpg\" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id=\"real_photo\" class=\"deal_contents\">\r\n<div id=\"title_real_photo\" class=\"block_title\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"description_images\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201305/b4fe5f09900746874556d2e332ac53d7.jpg\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201305/81d9318834db832b9f81be813de5085a.jpg\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201305/c76eaf7d35afaf90da818ee2982a3926.jpg\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201305/8e241224cc539e1763e4eb359ad6fc0c.jpg\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n&